-- Russia’s Micex to Extend Ruble Evening Trading by End of 2012
-- B y   K s e n i a   G a l o u c h k o
-- 2012-06-29T08:00:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-29/russia-s-micex-to-extend-ruble-evening-trading-by-end-of-2012.html
Russia ’s Micex-RTS Exchange plans to
introduce an evening currency-trading session by the end of this
year, Lev Bystrov, the exchange’s spokesman, said by e-mail.  The currency market committee of Russia’s benchmark
exchange recommended introducing an evening session from 7 p.m.
to 11:50 p.m. Moscow time, according to a statement on the
exchange’s website today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ksenia Galouchko in Moscow at 
